  "response": "Organic peanut butter does not necessarily need to be refrigerated, but it can be. If you prefer a firmer texture or want to extend its shelf life, you can store it in the refrigerator. However, if you keep it in a cool, dark place, it should remain fresh for several months. Just make sure to stir it well before use, as the oil may separate over time.",
